claim.claim-text:
An IGBT switch circuit, wherein the IGBT switch circuit comprises:
an IGBT circuit (2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016), comprising a bipolar junction transistor (T21) and a first diode (d21) connected in parallel, the IGBT circuit (2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016) serving as a modulating switch between an electric machine (200) and a load (100) thereof;
an active clamping protection circuit (P) coupled to the IGBT circuit (2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016);
a switch (S2) also being connected between the IGBT circuit (2011, 2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2016) and the protection circuit (P).
